&gt; 
&gt; I am sorry you feel I took your box design by using wood.  Maybe I will use a different stain on the next one.
&gt; 
&gt; I will get some videos of the different modes of operation on the o-scope., just so you can see for yourself, my circuit functions as I intended it too.
